reviews.review_text: a little better... Better than the night before but, still not that great.  Pretty standard stuff here.  Sounds like Jerry, and maybe Brent, forgot how to play One More Saturday Night.  Also the first time I've really heard Healy put the pitch shifter on Brent during Hey Pocky Way.  Song transitions are still weak.
11-7-87 Very good show. Nice sounding remaster by Charlie.
